et al. 31500
</emphasis>
; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[113,125,1680,1698]" pageId="17" pageNumber="168">E</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis box="[136,304,1680,1698]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="168">Wolhauser et al. 559</emphasis>
